      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a decent project or budget-friendly daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with some fading paint and various scratches, and the interior has visible wear on the seats and carpets. While it runs and drives, it will likely need some mechanical maintenance in the near future to ensure long-term reliability. It's an honest car that provides a solid foundation for the right buyer.",
